column1: Who will win the 2020 Golden Globe for Best Performance by an Actress in a Motion Picture - Drama?
column5: ['Cynthia Erivo (Harriet)', 'Scarlett Johansson (Marriage Story)', 'Saoirse Ronan (Little Women)', 'Charlize Theron (Bombshell)', 'Renée Zellweger (Judy)', 'A tie or other outcome']

column6: This is a true horse race of prominent actors in well-reviewed starring roles. Johansson seems to have a slight edge, but could be anybody's.
